# Keep this repository focused on the WordPress project.
#
# This .gitignore lives in api-bajoterra, while WordPress lives in
# app/public. Everything is ignored by default, then the WordPress tree
# is allowed.

*

!.gitignore
!app/
app/*
!app/public/
!app/public/**

# Local/generated noise.
logs/
app/public/**/*.log
app/public/**/.DS_Store
app/public/**/Thumbs.db
